focus attention on the facts of the case, which are strong. <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Democrats</ENAMEX> want to
divert attention to the significance of the case, which is weak. So <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Republicans</ENAMEX>
