the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">defendant</ENAMEX> (<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Clinton</ENAMEX>), whereas <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Democrats</ENAMEX> want to shift scrutiny to the
